{event name='contentHeaderNavigation'}
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/nav&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;

{@$form-&gt;getHtml()}

{include file='footer'}
</code></pre> <p>We will now only concentrate on the new parts compared to <code>personList.tpl</code>:</p> <ol> <li>We use the <code>$action</code> variable to distinguish between the languages items used for adding a person and for creating a person.</li> <li>Because of form builder, we only have to call <code>{@$form-&gt;getHtml()}</code> to generate all relevant output for the form.</li> </ol>

